downloadTitle: Internet Explorer 11 Language Packs for Windows 7 and Windows Server 2008 R2
downloadDescription: Download the latest version of Internet Explorer 11 Language Packs.
detailsSection:
The Internet Explorer 11 Language Packs install language specific resource files, allowing users to view the user interface (UI) of Internet explorer 11 in a different supported language. To use these language packs, you must install the matching OS language pack on Windows before proceeding.

Visit the Windows MUI/LIP Knowledge Center for more information.
systemRequirementsSection:
• Windows 7 Service Pack 1 and higher Service pack
  • Windows Server 2008 R2 Service Pack 1 and higher Service Pack
  1. The OS Language Pack for the desired language must be installed.
  2. Internet Explorer 11 must be installed.
installInstructionSection:
1. Click the Download button for your Language Pack to start the download, or choose a different language from the list of available Language Packs below and click Go.
  2. Do one of the following:
    • To start the installation immediately, click Open.
    • To copy the download to your computer for installation at a later time, click Save
